                        <provenance>
                            The latter part of the name of the original owner, as present in supplications, has regularly been erased 
                            and substituted, producing the name of a secondary owner
                            <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14625WalattaMaryam">Walatta Māryām</persName>. According to 
                            <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">138</citedRange></bibl>,
                            this manuscript shares the same history as <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt46">UppEt46</ref> and
                            <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt47">UppEt47</ref>: they were all owned by the same original owner and later
                            all passed into the ownership <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14625WalattaMaryam">Walatta Māryām</persName>. Based on
                            <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/UppEt46">UppEt46</ref>, the original owner can be
                            identified as <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14626WalattaAbiyaEgzi">Walatta Abiya Egzi</persName> (contrary to
                            the suggestion by <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">138</citedRange></bibl>,
                            reproduced in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PXAATHYN"><seg type="dataset"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:alvin"/><title level="m">Alvin: Plattform för digitala samlingar och digitaliserat kulturarv</title><date/><note type="url">https://www.alvin-portal.org/info/en/start.html</note></bibl>, that the original owner was called
                            <foreign xml:lang="gez">Walatta Dǝngǝl</foreign>).
                            At some point between <date when="1866">1866</date>
                            (when the first missionaries connected to Evangeliska fosterlandsstiftelsen arrived in Ethiopia) and
                            <date when="1928">1928</date> (when the manuscript was catalogued for the first time in Sweden),
                            the manuscript was acquired by an unknown missionary of
                            Evangeliska fosterlandsstiftelsen and brought to Sweden. For a while, 
                            it was kept at <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS1020EFSmissionsmuseum">Evangeliska Fosterlands-Stiftelsens etnografiska missionsmuseum</placeName> in 
                            Johannelund (Ulvsunda, <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC7456Stockholm">Stockholm</placeName>).
                        </provenance>
                        <acquisition>
                            According to <ref target="#e4"/>, the manuscript reached its current repository in <date when="1968"/>.
                        </acquisition>
                    </history>

